{
  "stem": "18626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had notification, almost the Germans came in on the 25th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it took, like, 3, 4 weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like, free, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they started building the fences already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had the plan made, where the ghetto would be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started grabbing Jews and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they start digging the holes where the poles are going to be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother didn't want to prepare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't want to believe that we've got to leave our house that she worked so hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were poor people killed that built our house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That she's going to leave the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She even start to cry, let them kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not going to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we begged her, and we kissed her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the last ones to enter the ghetto there was, I think, our family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because our house, the real house where we lived, was not far from the ghetto, where we were told that we are going to live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because when I was in the ghetto, I could look through the fence, and see my house through the fence, and see gentile people already living in my house, a family, and the children were playing croquet that my father used to turn for the toy stores before the war.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he used to sell the croquets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we left the ghetto, we didn't take the croquets with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew we are not going to play croquet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are not going to sell croquets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we left a big stack of croquets-- croquet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I used to look out for my house where I lived in the ghetto, and looked through the wires, while the guards were watching us, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't escape.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
